messages.content: The New Militia (TNM) was born after the collapse of The Militia (TM), a legendary group that once stood as a titan in ClanCom. Internal betrayal sparked a civil war that tore the old foundation apart. The aftermath was Fanto creating TNM. Full of new leaders and new potential, We now have the Militia Network alongside other decentralization techniques that prevent us from suffering the same fate that TM did.
